%% Mermaid sequence diagram suggestions
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant APIGW as API\ Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth\ Service
    participant Book as Booking\ Service
    participant DB as Database

    Client->>APIGW: POST /api/v1/bookings
    APIGW->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>APIGW: 200 OK
    APIGW->>Book: CreateBooking(command)
    Book->>DB: INSERT booking
    DB-->>Book: 201 Created
    Book-->>APIGW: BookingCreated
    APIGW-->>Client: 201 Created + body
